; The search query language uses a pltg System with posting-set operators.
; This should be formalized as a proper language definition with:
; - LANG_DOCS entries for each operator (and, or, not, in, near, etc.)
; - A searchable.pltg std module defining operator semantics
; - Cross-check: operator count in SearchSystem vs language definition
(derive stub-todo-search-language-system stub :using (stub))

